---
title: Spiced Chicken & Roast Pumpkin Toss with Dill-Parsley Mayo & Almonds
description: Bring some cosy vibes to your weeknight dinners with this meal! Juicy, seasoned chicken meets a colourful array of roasted veggies and a sprinkle of almonds for the perfect crunch. Drizzled with a herbaceous mayo, this dish is an harmonious medley of warm flavours. It’s hearty, wholesome and full of feel-good deliciousness!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*

